{"type": "article", "id": 45676, "title": "《花花公子》创始人去世，以及，Chanel 要来成都办秀 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-09-29T03:16:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 3250, "name": "Rick Owens"}, {"id": 1580, "name": "巴黎时装周"}, {"id": 44428, "name": "Masion Margiela"}, {"id": 9519, "name": "Thom Browne"}, {"id": 44341, "name": "colette"}, {"id": 2040, "name": "KENZO"}, {"id": 44339, "name": "Fenty Puma"}, {"id": 44429, "name": "PALACE"}, {"id": 686, "name": "adidas"}, {"id": 6306, "name": "花花公子"}, {"id": 992, "name": "Chanel"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 20, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170929110312TmQP2IiKNlGuAyOw.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.ftchinese.com/story/001074511\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>《花花公子》杂志创始人去世，享年 91 岁</strong></a> | 昨日，花花公子公司发表声明称，《花花公子》杂志的创办者 Hugh Hefner 在家中无疾而终，享年 91 岁。</p><p><a href=\"https://globenewswire.com/news-release/2017/09/27/1133717/0/en/Despite-Closures-Nearly-Three-Quarters-of-Consumers-Plan-To-Do-Most-of-their-Holiday-Shopping-in-Stores-According-to-AlixPartners-Survey.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>尽管实体零售遇冷，70% 的美国消费者在假日季仍打算去实体店购物</strong></a> | 据咨询公司 AlixPartners 在对超过 1000 名消费者的最新调查显示，有 70% 的美国消费者计划在实体店购买一半或以上的假日季物品。尽管零售商在这段时间仍然面临着关店的风险，但 AlixPartners 指出，美国今年的假日销售可能有 3.5％ 至 4.4% 的增长。</p><p><strong><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/chanel-reprise-cruise-show-chengdu-11007482/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Chanel 将来成都走秀</a></strong> | 11 月 7 日，Chanel 将在成都重现 2017/18 早春系列发布会。这并非是 Chanel 的成都首秀，2015 年，Chanel 曾经就携该年的秋冬高级成衣系列于南京和成都进行了两次发布。据称，这次发布会的重要性和规模与 2016 年在北京举办的“巴黎在罗马”高级手工坊系列发布会相当。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/9/palace-x-adidas-originals-oreardon\" rel=\"nofollow\">adidas 和 PALACE 的联名系列</a> O’Reardon 正式发布了。除了烫金的 PALACE logo 表明合作，以及加粗的“三条杠”之外，和 1996 年款的 O’Reardon 好像没什么区别。 </p><p>这双鞋于 9 月 29 日登陆 PALACE 全球门店，售价 95 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170929104524F6fK1vcDrQpg5kCZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170929104525r8zlSuiIEp97FnR0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709291045463pv1zKojPUd4WZfJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170929104526EblaxLK025iSrcyD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170929104526wSGVbHegkCxyJFpR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170929104546fcrW2oFqnBZ6EuOm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/9/thom-browne-colette-paris-takeover\" rel=\"nofollow\">Thom Browne </a>将在 10 月 2 日正式接管 colette。这个以灰色调著称的美国设计师品牌将带来超过 200 件包括男、女装在内的限定单品，来看看都有哪些： </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170929104659rSBbwM3yTeHPxfLn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170929104657EAHiup7nSI3bZhct.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170929104648NF7u30XRr8YxLyoc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170929104648SMN6kD5UHuLKTRJC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170929104647OiXKHuFTaREC5e8M.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170929104648C9XA8ZJG2tf3s0KQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170929104648VYTBq8ZkcQ6MaeNx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170929104650bqnX0ikmZKFTujzs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017092910465104En3Y8wUPs1BTvW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170929104651UQl65TjL1f8WAvcZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170929104652wLIKz8ba9Fm1OMp4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170929104653GudlqWBoicHJ5NAm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170929104653hz7HlM3gRAPaeivI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170929104653QKkzaDMCyxPHbosw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170929104653T2eLYo6qDcwQ7KAX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170929104654IWDQ5SNenma3x7oC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170929104655tJpYDx0bGdIPFsAo.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709291046558ADliHLBTMGeWqpI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170929104656K3YtIvk6yB7WsHnE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170929104657CKVrJSldsuImv8yQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170929104657gJLmTjX2BuxFQf4y.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709291046573UXSJKwvNmdQ8IsM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170929104658WO7UaM4YTEBhA8zZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>另外，colette 还与巴黎快餐品牌 Blend 合作，推出了名为 <a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/9/colette-blend-farewell-cheeseburger\" rel=\"nofollow\">Farewell</a> 的限量牛肉汉堡，这两款蓝色的汉堡将供应至 10 月 3 日。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170929104800hsWLtTv9kEw7d6pX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>Rihanna 推出了一双全新的<a href=\"https://hypebae.com/2017/9/rihanna-fenty-puma-pointy-creeper-patent-leather-dove-grey\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Pointy Creeper</a>。这双售价 17000 日元，有着超厚防滑鞋底的漆皮尖头鞋子目前可以在日本的买手店 atmos 买到了。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170929104605V6UjSzGWk9CMQoTE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665812\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170929104613t1h3VncRzi5sUXPN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709291046133rOhmc6zu9t1SJIo.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>巴黎时装周，<a href=\"https://popbee.com/fashion/runway-fashion/pfw-spring-2018-ready-to-wearkenzo-la-memento/\" rel=\"nofollow\">KENZO </a>的现任总监 Humberto Leon 及 Carol Lim 推出向品牌创始人致敬的第二个系列 Kenzo La Collection Memento。 </p><p>该系列主打牛仔和彩色印花，统一让模特穿上了中筒袜配果冻鞋，包袋系列看起来也不错。创意总监还把日本神话中的八尾大蛇搬到了舞台上，进行了一段传统的日本舞蹈表演。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170929104905kH6G5Kc7VzY4CxPs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170929104905eqkHnNYJMC4E627a.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170929104907zKg4LeBCXlJMOAs0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017092910490891oTciNSaHQFVXAf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017092910491182jeDGPd5vbkmwIy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170929104911n4v8A7r6Tp3wVfO9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170929104911cHPNStsu52Dn7kRf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170929104914RlI3v92xyBmcHdh7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709291049145eyh31JNpoTPRCI2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709291049151Db4o0PpuIi9EX6l.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170929104917JSfCPsV3tcMuNvyq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170929104917UWN87jH9hbQ0mYB6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170929104918cOxzNaS9b8DRdFwC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170929104918qiteQArISuFoZp4J.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><