" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170929104927dF0YKLmHWAR6kuIh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170929104928kzq7jKDCPGw8ZEsX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170929104928DKAP1h6JgjT2dQmn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170929104929lUrosJYmNPByeQV0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/shows-reviews/gallery/rick-owens-rtw-spring-11010313/#!41/rick-owens-rtw-spring-2018-40\" rel=\"nofollow\">Rick Owens</a> 的 2018 春夏系列很是前卫大胆，主题可能是“右腿受伤的模特”、“戴着枕头的病人”。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170929105803tJTwG3FZuOsmnovf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.503660\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170929105731on7Dl6P9amVwNzRJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170929105731T3MsSlKfaL0qJ2pE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.503660\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170929105732WJQO1d3Z80vN5lBr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.503660\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170929105733uKTo8JmbN7DjLMef.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170929105733aLfPCbpoIVX9qMh1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017092910573581NrifLklGdeBET4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.503660\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017092910573